Module gymmanager.gymproject3

Package gymmanager.gymproject3

package gymmanager.gymproject3
  • Class
    Description
    ClassSchedule
    Used to create new ClassSchedule objects that hold all fitness classes at all gym locations, and the number of classes.
    Constants
    Holds constant values for integers used in calculation of dates.
    Date
    Used to create new Date objects that can be compared.
    Family
    Used to create new Family objects that hold information for members with family tier membership.
    FitnessClass
    Used to create new Fitness Class objects that hold the name of the class and instructor, time, list of participants, and the size of the class.
    GymManagerController
    Controller for GymManager.fxml
    GymManagerMain
    Application driver
    Location
    Holds enumeration data for the five gym locations.
    Member
    Used to create new Member objects that hold member information.
    MemberDatabase
    Creates and maintains a database that holds members and can sort by name, expiration date, or county.
    Premium
    Used to create new Premium objects that hold information for members with premium tier membership.
    Time
    Holds enumeration data for the times that the fitness classes are held at.
